snippet.title: Let's Play - Megaman V (Gameboy) - 01 - Neptune & Venus - Upon a painted ocean.
snippet.description:
Hey look! Two water stages for the price of one! How awesome! Oh. Wait. Nevermind.

So those other videos I said about? Yeah, they kind of got ruined by major sound desyncing. So have a Gameboy game.

Volume levels are a little off. My bad. I seem to always misjudge them on the initial recordings.

Out of all the Gameboy Megaman titles, this is probably the easiest, but makes up for it by being all kinds of awesome. It also has one of the better weapon sets out of any Megaman game.

This is a "I can't remember this game" run, so I do not remember a damned thing about it. 

I also try several times to get over my phobia over using E-Tanks. I do not always succeed. Er, so, apologises in advance.
